The paper deals with deep learning approaches for semantic segmentation, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of ensembles and the exploration of different architectures and training settings suggest a focus on machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing techniques for text-based segmentation, which could potentially fall under computational linguistics (cs.CL).
